[Verse 1]
[C] Heart and [Am] soul, [F] I fell in [G] love with you,
[C] Heart and [Am] soul, the [F] way a [G] fool would do,
[C] Madly... [Am] [F]
Because you [G] held me [C] tight, [Am]
And stole a [F] kiss in the [G] night...

